│ conditionally calling formLCSSA only when there are exit PHI nodes to update, we avoid unnecessary LCSSA formation that could disrupt the control flow    │
│ when the exit block has no PHIs. This should preserve the correct control flow structure and ensure that the exit block remains reachable."})             │
